data.description:
Imagine waking up to the gentle ripples of the lake right outside your window, were the golden sunsets cast a warm glow on the water! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath offers more than just a residence, it's a gateway to a life of tranquility and natural beauty. Outside of being energy efficient this is the ultimate entertainment home. Huge open concept kitchen with a gas range top and open breakfast room. The living room opens to the kitchen with access to the backyard. Gas burning fireplace and high ceilings with upgraded doors throughout. Enjoy your primary suite with the bay window seating and spacious bath. Spacious secondary bedrooms. Enjoy kayaking, fishing and peaceful moments on your own private boat dock. All appliance stay!
